They've now extended the warning zone to about eight kilometers around Mount Semeru, but we're told that there's been no disruptions to flights because the ash hasn't gone that high in the air, the cloud pooling at one point some two kilometers above the mountain.

01:29:29.266 --> 01:29:32.597
Okay, they saw it.

01:29:32.597 --> 01:29:36.284
At least it went while the video was playing.

01:29:48.800 --> 01:29:49.173
You have to watch them.

01:29:49.173 --> 01:29:54.640
At least you can see the video.

01:30:09.520 --> 01:30:10.874
I don't know what's been going on; we'll get a new phone or something.

01:30:10.874 --> 01:30:23.910
It's happened a lot lately.

01:30:24.200 --> 01:30:26.439
It keeps messing up, but it's okay.

01:30:26.439 --> 01:30:30.427
This too shall pass.

01:30:30.427 --> 01:30:33.580
What do you think's causing that?

01:30:40.351 --> 01:30:40.575
I don't know; it's so weird.

01:30:40.575 --> 01:30:42.578
All right, let's take communion together.

01:30:42.578 --> 01:30:43.893
Resistance—it's just resistance.

01:31:09.787 --> 01:31:10.453
You know you're on the right road when you get resistance.

01:31:15.643 --> 01:31:16.327
I say, "Woo!

01:31:19.060 --> 01:31:19.743
I like it!

01:31:19.743 --> 01:31:27.440
" Father, I thank You, Lord, that we take the devil off.

01:31:30.697 --> 01:31:33.806
You know that, Father, we are never called to be in with the crowd.

01:31:33.806 --> 01:31:38.380
Father, we're called to separate ourselves from the crowd.

01:31:38.380 --> 01:31:42.616
Father, we stand with the King.

01:31:46.697 --> 01:31:47.143
No guts, no glory, no newsletter story.

01:31:47.143 --> 01:31:51.199
I loved it when he said that, Brandon.

01:31:51.725 --> 01:31:53.302
It takes guts.

01:32:11.299 --> 01:32:11.714
You either have it or you don't.

01:32:11.714 --> 01:32:18.907
Either you stand outside of the crowd or you don't.

01:32:18.907 --> 01:32:21.920
No guts, no glory, no newsletter story.

01:32:29.376 --> 01:32:29.664
You either stand or you don't, son.

01:32:29.664 --> 01:32:33.320
I said, "Okay, I get it.

01:32:33.320 --> 01:32:37.886
" As the storm winds blow all around me, I stand.

01:32:37.886 --> 01:32:48.867
When all there is else to do is stand, stand therefore.

01:32:48.867 --> 01:32:59.886
And I thank You, Father, for the body, that I can stand boldly in Your throne room.

01:32:59.886 --> 01:33:05.667
Father, I thank You, Lord, that I'm made in the image of Jesus.

01:33:05.667 --> 01:33:15.576
As He is, so are we in this world.

01:33:22.029 --> 01:33:22.379
And Father, I thank You that Christ in me is the hope of glory today.

01:33:29.685 --> 01:33:30.674
I thank You, Lord, that You show us that which is to come.

01:33:30.674 --> 01:33:58.346
Father, I thank You that even if we miss it because we are human, we stand up, we brush ourselves off, and we keep marching.

01:33:58.346 --> 01:34:04.240
Onward Christian soldiers!

01:34:04.240 --> 01:34:06.773
Don't lie down and feel bad.

01:34:06.773 --> 01:34:09.371
No, we keep our eyes vertical.

01:34:09.371 --> 01:34:14.062
We keep our eyes focused on Jesus today.

01:34:17.840 --> 01:34:21.680
And we thank You, Lord, that we're not moved by what we see.

01:34:21.680 --> 01:34:27.635
We're not moved by what we feel.

01:34:27.635 --> 01:34:35.800
We're moved by what the Word of God says.

01:34:42.360 --> 01:34:42.800
And Father, I thank You, Lord.

01:35:06.759 --> 01:35:18.093
We fear You today, and we seek You, and You said we would find You.

01:35:18.093 --> 01:35:32.880
We take this body in the name of Jesus, and we're healed and whole and well in the mighty name of Jesus.

01:35:32.880 --> 01:35:36.631
Thank You, Lord, for Diana, Braden, and my girls.

01:35:36.631 --> 01:35:46.240
Father, I thank You, Lord, that the blood of Jesus Christ covers us from the top of our heads to the soles of our feet.

01:36:00.297 --> 01:36:00.743
And we thank You, Father, for Your mighty provision over us.

01:36:05.760 --> 01:36:06.960
You supply all our needs according to Your riches in glory by Christ Jesus.

01:36:06.960 --> 01:36:09.140
Father, You heal us by Your stripes.

01:36:09.140 --> 01:36:10.010
You provide.

01:36:10.010 --> 01:36:11.880
You take care of us.

01:36:11.880 --> 01:36:14.240
Father, You are our provision.

01:36:14.240 --> 01:36:20.059
You're our protector, our healer, and our deliverer.

01:36:33.800 --> 01:36:33.980
And we thank You, Lord, that You are our abundant supply in every area of our life—spiritually, physically, mentally, emotionally, financially—everything.

01:36:40.035 --> 01:36:42.426
You have done it all.

01:36:46.457 --> 01:36:49.760
And we thank You, Father, that we rest in You, and we will tell the people that You're coming.

01:36:49.760 --> 01:36:55.520
We'll tell it with boldness and we won't shrink back like cowards.

01:36:55.520 --> 01:36:57.199
Father, I thank You, Lord.

01:36:57.199 --> 01:37:06.666
We take this body in the name of Jesus; You paid a price and You paid it all.

01:37:06.666 --> 01:37:10.079
I humbly give all to You, Lord.

01:37:10.079 --> 01:37:14.160
All to Jesus, I surrender all today.

01:37:14.160 --> 01:37:17.165
We surrender, Lord, in Jesus' mighty name.

01:37:17.165 --> 01:37:18.512
Amen and amen.

01:37:18.512 --> 01:37:22.657
Father, we thank You, Lord.

01:37:22.667 --> 01:37:27.485
Lord, we thank You for the blood.

01:37:27.485 --> 01:37:36.662
We pour the blood and we make much of the blood, and the blood makes much of us.

01:37:36.891 --> 01:37:45.536
And Father, I thank You, Lord, that we have the fresh Rhema, fresh.

01:37:45.536 --> 01:37:49.257
We're not on stagnant word that's 40 years old.

01:37:49.257 --> 01:37:51.460
Father, we go from glory to glory.

01:37:51.460 --> 01:38:01.476
We have fresh Rhema word that comes right out of the mouth of the Father every single day because we sit at Your feet daily.

01:38:01.476 --> 01:38:17.696
Not just when we visit every once in a while, but God, we're children that sit at Your throne daily.

01:38:17.696 --> 01:38:20.840
And we take the blood.

01:38:35.300 --> 01:38:37.800
I apply the blood over my wife, I apply the blood over me, and I apply the blood over my son.

01:38:37.800 --> 01:38:41.848
Father, we thank You, Lord.

01:38:41.848 --> 01:38:47.420
We make much of the blood, and the blood makes much of us.

01:39:16.520 --> 01:39:16.780
Like Sister Billie would say, "O Father, we make much of the blood, and the blood makes much of us.

01:39:16.780 --> 01:39:20.159
" For we are in Him.

01:39:20.159 --> 01:39:23.040
We are in You.

01:39:23.040 --> 01:39:25.559
We are in Christ Jesus.

01:39:25.559 --> 01:39:32.169
Thank you, Lord, for the blood.

01:39:32.169 --> 01:39:33.933
Thank you, Lord, for the blood.

01:39:33.933 --> 01:39:41.542
And we take the blood, Father, right now in the mighty name of Jesus.

01:39:41.542 --> 01:39:50.667
And we give You all the glory, honor, and praise for washing us, making us cleansed from all our sin.

01:39:50.667 --> 01:39:53.063
All of it is gone.

01:39:53.063 --> 01:39:58.720
"Behold," He said, "I make all things new.

01:39:58.720 --> 01:40:01.889
" Thank you, Lord, for the blood right now in Jesus' name.

01:40:03.519 --> 01:40:04.987
I plead the blood over my spiritual eyes.

01:40:11.030 --> 01:40:32.834
I plead the blood over my eyes that I am uninterrupted and unhindered by any satanic or demonic force.

01:40:33.543 --> 01:40:44.800
I plead the blood over my eyes tonight, Father, and I anoint myself with oil, and my cup runneth over.

01:40:59.812 --> 01:41:00.506
I thank You, Lord, that I hear You, God.

01:41:01.199 --> 01:41:05.029
I plead the blood over my spiritual eyes.

01:41:05.623 --> 01:41:32.710
And I thank You, Lord, that if there's anything You want to show us tonight, that which is to come, we have it uninterrupted and unhindered by any satanic or demonic spirit.

01:41:32.710 --> 01:41:44.533
Father, I thank You, Lord, that You speak through my vocal cords and You think through my mind.

01:41:44.533 --> 01:42:01.899
None of me and all of You, in the mighty name of Jesus, we pray.

01:42:01.899 --> 01:42:03.419
Amen and amen.

01:42:04.590 --> 01:42:08.010
And we plead the blood over Diana, Lord.

01:42:13.555 --> 01:42:13.973
And I thank You that You show her.

01:42:13.973 --> 01:42:18.537
I want to put on your mantle, love.

01:42:21.679 --> 01:42:22.399
I lay hands on you.

01:42:27.906 --> 01:42:28.719
I sure love you.

01:42:28.719 --> 01:42:34.213
Father, we plead the blood over us.

01:42:34.213 --> 01:42:36.760
Father, we thank You.

01:42:44.920 --> 01:42:49.679
I feel the Holy Ghost and fire on me.

01:42:49.679 --> 01:42:50.692
Hallelujah.

01:42:50.692 --> 01:42:52.106
Hallelujah.

01:42:52.106 --> 01:42:54.971
Isn't Jesus wonderful?

01:42:54.971 --> 01:43:01.813
Isn't He wonderful as the storm winds blow all around you?

01:43:01.813 --> 01:43:16.586
Isn't Jesus wonderful when you're not in popular opinion, and you stand all by yourself and the winds are blowing and people are throwing tomatoes at you?

01:43:35.700 --> 01:43:35.1000
You say, "Oh, but God is so good to me.

01:43:35.1000 --> 01:43:45.759
" But God is able to do exceedingly abundantly above all that we dare ask or think.

01:44:01.461 --> 01:44:02.366
He is able.

01:44:02.366 --> 01:44:06.448
He is able.

01:44:06.448 --> 01:44:12.142
For the Lord, He is good, and His mercy endures forever.

01:44:12.142 --> 01:44:15.920
Great is Your faithfulness to us, O God.

01:44:15.920 --> 01:44:23.920
Great is Your faithfulness to my household.

01:44:23.920 --> 01:44:30.711
Father, as for me and my house, we will serve the Lord, even when it's not politically correct.

01:44:30.711 --> 01:44:37.943
We are all going to be on Your side.

01:44:37.943 --> 01:44:40.400
For who is on the Lord's side?

01:44:40.400 --> 01:44:58.920
Me, my wife, my children, Father.

01:44:58.920 --> 01:45:06.074
For there are more with us than there are with them.

01:45:06.074 --> 01:45:29.328
As we look out on the hillside, there's more that is with us than there are with them.

01:45:29.338 --> 01:45:44.320
We don't care what they say, for we have more with us than there are with them.

01:45:44.320 --> 01:45:45.940
Jesus Christ is coming.

01:45:45.940 --> 01:45:46.860
He's coming.

01:45:46.860 --> 01:45:50.180
Open the eyes of my heart, Lord.

01:45:50.180 --> 01:45:52.939
Open the eyes of my heart.

01:45:52.939 --> 01:45:56.030
Open the eyes to see His face.

01:45:56.030 --> 01:46:04.880
O Father, the fire in our bones, just like fire in our bones.

01:46:04.880 --> 01:46:11.253
Holy Ghost and fire shut up in our bones.

01:46:11.253 --> 01:46:23.439
It's just like fire, shut up in my bones.

01:46:23.439 --> 01:46:27.269
That Holy Ghost fire, shut up in my bones.

01:46:27.269 --> 01:46:28.686
Thank you, Lord.

01:46:28.686 --> 01:46:34.320
First it was fragrance and then it turned to fire.

01:46:34.320 --> 01:46:36.320
My worship is my weapon.

01:46:37.987 --> 01:46:40.768
This is how I win my battles.

01:46:40.768 --> 01:46:59.472
First it was fragrance and then it turned to fire.

01:46:59.472 --> 01:47:02.719
My worship is my weapon.

01:47:16.320 --> 01:47:16.980
This is how I win my battles.

01:47:16.980 --> 01:47:20.940
I love that song.

01:47:20.940 --> 01:47:25.829
First it was fragrance, then it turned to fire.

01:47:25.829 --> 01:47:27.531
My worship is my weapon.

01:47:43.623 --> 01:47:44.069
This is how I win my battle.

01:47:56.560 --> 01:47:56.720
I feel His presence so strong.

01:47:56.720 --> 01:47:58.479
Thank you, Father, for Your fragrance.

01:47:58.479 --> 01:48:16.045
Thank you, Father, that it turned to fire.

01:48:16.045 --> 01:48:22.220
Thank you, Lord, that my worship is my weapon.

01:48:22.220 --> 01:48:24.480
This is how I win my battles.

01:48:24.480 --> 01:48:27.519
Thank you, Lord.

01:48:27.519 --> 01:48:28.319
Thank you, Father.

01:48:28.319 --> 01:48:29.759
He said, "Look into Me today.

01:48:29.759 --> 01:48:30.790
Look into Me today.

01:48:30.790 --> 01:48:32.760
" Then He said, "Look into Me.

01:48:32.760 --> 01:48:34.920
Look how I look.

01:48:34.920 --> 01:48:36.930
Look into Me today.

01:48:36.930 --> 01:48:39.920
" I see the sun arising upon Africa today.

01:48:39.920 --> 01:48:42.937
I see the fire.

01:48:42.937 --> 01:48:43.440
I see the glory.

01:48:43.440 --> 01:48:46.569
I see the rays of the sun shining upon the people.

01:48:46.569 --> 01:48:47.679
Might open up.

01:48:47.679 --> 01:48:53.737
I see the sun shining on their faces today.

01:48:53.737 --> 01:49:00.400
I see the African people with their faces looking toward the sun.

01:49:18.400 --> 01:49:19.100
But there's a glory; in this vision, I see it's olive oil.

01:49:19.100 --> 01:49:24.840
There's oil, the Holy Ghost oil, running down their faces.

01:49:24.840 --> 01:49:28.080
They're dressed in African garb with tribal beads.

01:49:28.080 --> 01:49:32.800
There's red on these outfits, but they have these headdresses on.

01:49:37.235 --> 01:49:47.750
But as they're looking toward the sun, I see a new oil running down their faces and there's a glory on their faces.

01:49:50.000 --> 01:49:54.680
And there's nothing around but just like dirt and these huts.

01:49:54.680 --> 01:50:01.1000
But as this glory is falling down there, there's oil falling down on their faces.

01:50:27.920 --> 01:50:28.373
It's saturating them.

01:50:38.149 --> 01:50:45.755
It's like whenever you dump oil, it spreads, and the glory of the Lord is coming upon the African people.

01:50:54.800 --> 01:50:55.074
It's interesting.

01:50:55.074 --> 01:50:56.171
I see them.

01:51:12.639 --> 01:51:13.016
They're jumping and they're putting their chests out.

01:51:13.016 --> 01:51:15.280
They're making a noise.

01:51:15.280 --> 01:51:17.333
They're popping their chests back.

01:51:17.333 --> 01:51:19.120
It's like a dance.

01:51:19.120 --> 01:51:29.375
But they have beads on and there's paint on them.

01:51:29.375 --> 01:51:34.360
But there's olive oil coming down on them.

01:51:44.286 --> 01:51:44.594
He's not forgotten you today.

01:51:44.594 --> 01:51:48.461
Many think, "Well, what about—where's the revival for Africa?

01:51:48.461 --> 01:51:53.800
Where's the coming of the King?

01:51:53.800 --> 01:51:57.199
Where is the Lord?

01:52:08.440 --> 01:52:08.800
There's been so much drought here.

01:52:12.309 --> 01:52:12.579
" And I see the drought.

01:52:27.200 --> 01:52:27.440
But I hear the sound of an abundance of rain.

01:52:27.440 --> 01:52:29.959
I hear the sound of an abundance of rain.

01:52:29.959 --> 01:52:32.137
I hear it's like a ticking noise.

01:52:45.485 --> 01:52:45.943
I'm going to go in a deeper realm.

01:52:45.943 --> 01:52:47.300
Glory to God.

01:52:47.300 --> 01:52:51.820
He says, "Glory to God, even down into the Congo.

01:52:51.820 --> 01:52:52.420
" That's what He just said.

01:52:52.420 --> 01:52:55.893
Even down into the Congo, with great persecution.

01:52:55.893 --> 01:52:59.280
You're going to see, I'm telling you, creative miracles.

01:52:59.280 --> 01:53:01.199
This is going to be a wave.

01:53:08.880 --> 01:53:11.760
A wave will come and it will pull, and another wave will come right on the heels of it, of the creative miracles.

01:53:11.760 --> 01:53:19.480
You're about to see a wave, a wave, a wave of the glory upon this world.

01:53:19.480 --> 01:53:27.109
It will come in waves and it will look like that one's receding back, but another wave will come.

01:53:42.137 --> 01:53:42.583
And as these waves keep coming in, I see arms.

01:53:42.583 --> 01:53:48.010
I see in the wave of this glory.

01:53:48.010 --> 01:53:50.605
I see body parts in the wave.

01:54:01.410 --> 01:54:01.740
The wave comes in and it recedes back.

01:54:01.740 --> 01:54:07.309
But before it even has time to recede back, another glory wave comes in.

01:54:07.309 --> 01:54:13.130
But in this wave are eyes, ears, hands, feet—body parts from My reserves are coming unto thee.

01:54:17.908 --> 01:54:18.216
And there will be creative miracles flowing in Africa.

01:54:18.216 --> 01:54:22.296
There will be creative miracles flowing in America.

01:54:22.296 --> 01:54:25.909
You will see it as you yield to it.

01:54:25.909 --> 01:54:29.949
I see a Holy Ghost wave of glory flowing in South America.

01:54:29.949 --> 01:54:39.451
I see it hitting all out in the bush, in the glorious, and you will see the glory of the Lord.

01:54:48.160 --> 01:54:48.400
The glory of the Lord will wash over the people.

01:54:48.400 --> 01:54:51.120
It will look like a washing and a flow.

01:54:51.120 --> 01:54:53.268
It will flow and flow.

01:54:58.889 --> 01:54:59.199
And the glory, unlike you have ever seen before, the glory of the Lord.

01:55:12.159 --> 01:55:12.415
I hear the Lord say it will be a flow.

01:55:12.415 --> 01:55:27.799
I see the eyes, the ears, and the toes, what you have been believing for from these great silos, for I am emptying them out for I do not need them here.

01:55:41.938 --> 01:55:42.169
I hear Him say, "What more do you need to hear?

01:55:45.689 --> 01:55:51.147
" He said, "I have reserved it for today, for a great move of My presence will be upon My people today.

01:55:51.147 --> 01:56:07.370
I will empty the reserves, for there is no need for it here, for this was what I called, and it will draw you near.

01:56:07.370 --> 01:56:13.759
For it is My goodness," He says, "that will bring them to repentance.

01:56:13.759 --> 01:56:16.133
For it is My goodness that will pass through.

01:56:16.648 --> 01:56:25.459
You will see My goodness and My mercy—something you did not earn and something you did not deserve.

01:56:25.459 --> 01:56:26.239
For My glory.

01:56:37.543 --> 01:56:37.920
I hear the sound of abundance of rain, for it will be the glory unto Him.

01:56:52.719 --> 01:56:53.153
I am emptying My silos; they are dumping them out.

01:57:03.383 --> 01:57:03.657
I see it will come in on the waves, a wave of the glory.

01:57:03.657 --> 01:57:06.719
There will be so much of this.

01:57:06.719 --> 01:57:10.320
I see black arms, white arms, brown arms, and yellow arms—creative miracles.

01:57:10.320 --> 01:57:14.411
Blue eyes, black eyes, brown eyes, and green eyes.

01:57:14.411 --> 01:57:26.250
As you walk in My authority, I see the glory and I see more healings of hearts, livers, and intestines.

01:57:26.250 --> 01:57:28.139
I see brand new colons.

01:57:48.959 --> 01:57:49.319
You might have a colostomy bag, but He is going to restore back what the cankerworm ate.

01:57:49.319 --> 01:57:52.132
He said, "There will be no sick among you.

01:57:52.132 --> 01:58:20.200
" Just like My children of Israel, they left with no sickness and no disease.

01:58:20.880 --> 01:58:23.066
You will walk in the same.

01:58:23.066 --> 01:58:30.639
It will be a type and and shadow.

01:58:30.639 --> 01:58:34.720
You would have to resist the glory.

01:58:34.720 --> 01:58:39.408
This is an outpouring over Africa, South America, and America.

01:59:04.320 --> 01:59:04.617
He says, "America, get out of the thinking of the natural.

01:59:04.617 --> 01:59:17.350
" If you resist this—I see Africa, and it is happening like ripe cherries off a tree.

01:59:26.408 --> 01:59:28.400
It is happening so much in the middle for the people who would just believe.

01:59:28.400 --> 01:59:37.088
America tries to block it like a dam because of the tradition of man.

01:59:37.088 --> 01:59:41.960
Get out of the natural thinking.

01:59:41.960 --> 01:59:45.013
Come up higher with Me.

01:59:45.013 --> 01:59:48.231
Do not be a dam; be a river.

01:59:48.231 --> 01:59:51.395
Let Him flow.

01:59:51.395 --> 01:59:56.098
Let the Holy Ghost flow.

01:59:56.098 --> 02:00:00.600
Let Him flow like He can in Africa.

02:00:00.600 --> 02:00:03.340
Let Him flow through South America.

02:00:14.411 --> 02:00:14.662
I see the glory of the Lord.

02:00:17.467 --> 02:00:18.240
I see the waves.

02:00:18.240 --> 02:00:51.253
Before the wave is able to come back, another wave will come on top of it, for I am emptying My silos.

02:00:54.800 --> 02:00:55.022
There is too much religion for today.

02:00:55.022 --> 02:00:56.578
Let the Holy Ghost flow.

02:00:56.578 --> 02:00:59.337
Let the Holy Spirit flow.

02:01:22.719 --> 02:01:23.313
It is His goodness and His mercy that will follow us.

02:01:29.280 --> 02:01:31.623
This is the great finale that He has for us, the greatest finale of all.

02:01:37.360 --> 02:01:37.540
